Spanish /ˈspænɪʃ/

1. ADJ Spanish means belonging or relating to Spain, or to its people, language, or culture. 西班牙(人)的; 西班牙语的; 西班牙文化的 [usu ADJ n] 

例： ...a Spanish sherry. ...一瓶西班牙雪利酒。 

例： ...the Spanish ambassador. ...西班牙大使。 

2. N-UNCOUNT Spanish is the main language spoken in Spain, and in many countries in South and Central America. 西班牙语 

3. N-PLURAL The Spanish are the people who come from Spain. 西班牙人 [usu 'the' N]

